hermes-flake
============

This repository is a third-party Nix packaging of `hermes-agent`.

`hermes-agent` is the work of NousResearch:

  https://github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent
  https://nousresearch.com

The `hermes-agent` source is fetched at the upstream-tagged commit and built
unmodified — this flake does not patch the agent's code. All credit for the
agent itself belongs to NousResearch.

This wrapper repository contributes:

  - A `nix2nix`-compatible derivation (uv2nix) that reproduces hermes-agent
    builds from upstream's `uv.lock`.
  - NixOS service module (`services.hermes-agent`).
  - Wrapper modules for systemd-nspawn containers, podman/docker, and
    microvm.nix VMs.
  - A home-manager module for per-user installs.
  - Documentation describing NixOS-specific integration patterns (sops-nix,
    btrfs subvolumes, EnvironmentFile, isolation trade-offs).

This wrapper is NOT endorsed by, sponsored by, or affiliated with NousResearch.

For bugs / feature requests:

  - In the agent itself  → https://github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent
  - In the Nix packaging → https://github.com/ErikBPF/hermes-flake

